$PAR
Assume that \( u \cdotp v = $v0 \), \( \| u \| = $v1 \), and \( \| v \| = $v2 \).
$PAR
What is the value of \( $w0 u \cdotp ( $vstr ) \)?
$PAR
\{ans_rule()\}
